   "source": [
    "\n",
    "# 9) Function List (What you will implement)\n",
    "\n",
    "Fill in a function list that matches the design:\n",
    "\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# State initialization\n",
    "create_board()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Display\n",
    "display_board(board)\n",
    "clear_screen()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Inspection functions\n",
    "is_valid_move(board, row, col)\n",
    "check_winner(board)\n",
    "game_over(board)\n",
    "current_player(board)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Decision logic\n",
    "get_human_move(board)\n",
    "get_computer_move(board)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Transition (mutates state)\n",
    "place_move(board, row, col, player)\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
  },
