    "\n",
    "# Exit Ticket (2 minutes)\n",
    "\n",
    "1) If the program dies, What must be saved for the game to be continued? (given X always starts)?\n",
    "\n",
    "Just the board. You can derive whose turn it is by counting X's and O's.\n",
    "\n",
    "2) What is one invariant you will enforce in `is_valid_move` or `place_move`?\n",
    "\n",
    "In is_valid_move I'll check that the cell is empty (contains ' ') before allowing the move. This enforces the invariant that you cant overwrite an existing X or O.\n"
